A '''Republic Peace Officer''' was a [[Police officer/Legends|police officer]] in the [[Judicial Department/Legends|Judicial Department's]] [[Republic Security Force/Legends|Republic Guard]] during the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].<ref name="SWRG RCR">''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Revised Core Rulebook]]''</ref> This term was descriptive of a person's career field in [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|law enforcement]] and was not used as an individual rank.

